# Enforce LF line endings for the bundled GitHub Action dist so that
# cross-platform rebuilds (macOS arm64, Linux x64, Windows) produce
# deterministic output for the `Action dist freshness` CI check.
#
# The tslib runtime helpers bundled into dist/index.mjs by ncc contain
# CRLF in their upstream source. Without this normalization, macOS builds
# retain the CR characters while git's `autocrlf=input` strips them on
# commit, causing every CI build to show a phantom diff.
runners/github-action/dist/*.mjs text eol=lf
runners/github-action/dist/*.map text eol=lf
runners/github-action/dist/*.cjs text eol=lf
